    answer: `The WhatsApp add-on is £${pricing.addOn.price}/month as a channel add-on. A domestic 12-panel system with battery generates £8,000 to £14,000. A commercial 100kWp system generates £60,000 to £100,000. Securing one homeowner's GivEnergy survey through a rapid WhatsApp response — while you mounted panels on another roof — covers the annual channel cost from a single installation.`
  },
  {
    question: "Can I take over a WhatsApp conversation?",
    answer: "Reply once in any thread and the AI relinquishes control permanently. Most solar installers let the AI gather the initial scope — roof orientation, tile type, shading, consumption, battery preference, and EV ownership — then take over to discuss panel layout, inverter selection, and the survey date."
  },
